00:02:15.789 --> 00:02:23.789
Contemplating on Noah, it gave her the courage to fulfill her assignment because she, like Noah, did just so.

00:02:23.789 --> 00:02:28.789
The scripture says, the blessings of Jehovah, that is what makes rich.

00:02:28.789 --> 00:02:36.789
That is so true. We could have stayed in Jersey in our little apartment, maybe even by now have a comfortable living.

00:02:36.789 --> 00:02:41.789
But what really makes life living is the people and friends you have.

00:02:41.789 --> 00:02:45.789
As it was once said, you can't outgive Jehovah.

00:02:45.789 --> 00:02:53.789
If anyone is considering the going through a door that Jehovah has opened up for them, I don't hesitate.

00:02:53.789 --> 00:03:09.550
You've got the support of Jehovah, unseen angels, his spirit, and the brotherhood, and the blessings are just waiting for you.

